    "extract": "Funko Fusion is a 2024 crossover action-adventure game developed and published by 10:10 Games. The game is based on the \"Funko Pop!\" toy line created by Funko.\nFunko Fusion was released for PlayStation 5, Windows, and Xbox Series X/S on September 13, 2024. The game was also released for PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch on December 6. It received mixed reviews from critics and was a commercial failure which lead to layoffs at 10:10 Games."
